    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@ellisonbg \nWhat are the advantages of doing the \"checkbox --> drop-down menu\" versus just having a drop-down menu at every notebook?\n\nI would think its is more convenient for a user to have a drop down at every notebook. It only requires once action (i.e. pick from drop down menu) vs. two actions (i.e. check a box and then pick from drop down menu). \n\nI understand there is an advantage of doing an action on multiple notebooks at once. Is this what we want to support?\n"
